description: My place is close to Central Park North (110 St), 6 Train (will take you downtown in 15 minutes).
name: Cozy East Harlem Apartment
review: Marenika was very welcoming and a quick communicator. She treated us like friends and provided a clean, spacious space for us to stay in. The place is also in close proximity to Line 6 so it's a great place if you're going to frequent the subway.
